Ambassador: Tamron, Samyang, Nisi, Sirui, Lowepro, Lexar, Pentax. Partner: Focus Nordic. Samsung S10+ ambassador. Columnist DIY Photography. A 55 year old Norwegian math teacher who fell in love with photography when he received his first camera as a birthday present in January 2013.

10 ECs 500px

5 ECs Fstoppers

3 silver and 1 bronze Epson Pano Awards (2017)
